msgid "Please set the minimum value to a value less than the maximum value."
msgstr "最小値は最大値より小さい値を設定してください。"

#: inc/filter-search-pro/package/src/custom-field-search-pro/edit.js:984
msgid "Please enter a number."
msgstr "数値を入力してください。"

#: inc/filter-search-pro/package/src/custom-field-search-pro/edit.js:989
#: inc/filter-search-pro/package/src/post-date-search-pro/edit.js:430
msgid "Please enter a date in the format \"YYYY–MM–DD\". (e.g. 2020–01–01)"
msgstr "“YYYY-MM-DD”. の形式で入力してください。（例:2020-01-01）"

#: inc/filter-search-pro/package/src/custom-field-search-pro/edit.js:994
msgid ""
"Please enter a date and time in the format \"YYYY–MM–DD hh:mm:ss\". (e.g. "
"2020–01–01 00:00:00)"
msgstr ""
"日付と時刻を「YYYY–MM–DD hh:mm:ss」の形式で入力してください。（例：2020–01–"
"01 00:00:00）"

#: inc/filter-search-pro/package/src/custom-field-search-pro/edit.js:999
msgid "Please enter a time in the format \"hh:mm:ss\". (e.g. 00:00:00)"
msgstr "“hh:mm:ss”. の形式で入力してください。（例:00:00:00）"

